  "description": "<p><strong>Finance & Business Intern</strong></p><p><strong>$1200</strong><br /></p><p>To apply or find out more, please contact<br /><br /><strong>Leong Jia Wei </strong>(Reg No: R25157456) on WhatsApp <strong>+65 80358497 </strong>or email <a href=\"mailto:jiawei@placement.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">jiawei@placement.com.sg<br /></a></p><p>Calling All Students in Finance, Business & Other Fields for an invaluable internship during 25 May to 13 July 2026.</p><p><br /><strong>Get Paid $1,200 + Win up to $1,500 + Overseas Business Camp!</strong></p><p>Embark on a Hands-On Immersion Programme for tertiary students who want real exposure to finance, leadership, and business.</p><p>Learn from industry executives, obtain the <strong>CMFAS certification</strong> and gain invaluable experience for future roles.</p><p><strong>What you’ll get:</strong></p><p> $1,200 paid allowance<br /> 1-on-1 mentorship with industry leaders<br /> Awards & prizes worth up to $1,500<br /> Fully sponsored overseas business camp<br /> Certificate of completion + resume boost</p><p><strong>Who this is for:</strong></p><p> Singaporean Citizens (SG) and Permanent Resident (PR) Tertiary Students with A-Levels / Local Diploma<br /> Curious, motivated students who want mentorship and real-world experience<br /></p><p><br /></p>",
